description: President U Htin Kyaw of Myanmar took the oath of office on Wednesday and pledged to improve living standards in a speech to both houses of the country’s Parliament.
title: Myanmar’s President Speaks After Inauguration
title_page: Myanmar’s President Speaks After Inauguration - Video - NYTimes.com
text: President U Htin Kyaw of Myanmar took the oath of office on Wednesday and pledged to improve living standards in a speech to both houses of the country’s Parliament.
